</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_142" id="70r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_142_r2l1"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Gareyſen <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Dyetfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_142_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> yoſep Juden ʒu Dyetfurt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l3">geſeſſen / vnd <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Juden bey vns wonhaft etc Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l4"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Juden für vns beſandt vnd mıt Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l5">fleıſſıg <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / mug Jn der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> yoſep </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l6">Jud ʒuſprüch nıht erlaſſen / ſo well er Jm <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l7">des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ın der maſſe als er Jm vor <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l8">hab / Oder vor der Jüdıſcheıt bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / ſey <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> das dem yoſep </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l9">
<add><ab facs="#facs_142_r1l1"><expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> niht <expan>füklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo ſprıcht <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Jud / er oder ſein voller gewalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l10"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> der ſache gen <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> yoſep <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu awſʒtrag <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l11">der Juden <expan>Hohmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> einem ʒu Bamberg oder ʒu Eger Denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_line_1577034599747_2631">wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> vdalrıcȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_142" id="70r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Gareysen, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu Dyetfurt</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Yosep juden zu Dyetfurt gesessen und
                                <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> juden bey uns wonhaft etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> juden für uns besandt und mit im fleissig
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt; der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, mug in der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Yosep jud zusprüch niht erlassen,
                        so well er im <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, in der masse als er im vor
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> hab, oder vor der jüdischeit bey
                        uns zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. Sey <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        das dem Yosep <add><expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan></add> niht
                                <expan>füklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so spricht
                                <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> jud, er oder sein voller gewalt
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> der sache gen
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Yosep
                            <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu awsztrag <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vor
                        der juden <expan>hohmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> einem zu Bamberg oder zu Eger.
                        Denn wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Udalrici.</ab>
</div>
